JOIN MY TEAM TODAY! 💕 custom meal plans & workouts to suit YOU, your lifestyle & goals! -
My approach to nutrition & training is all about creating a lifestyle that you can sustain. 💞
-
This means NO excessive hours of cardio or time in the gym, low calories, extremes like no carb or no fat diets, no missing out of social events, no anxiety over food. I’ve been there and no how bad excessive and obsessive behaviours toward training can be. It impacts not only you and your health (mentally & physically) but it impacts your relationships. 💥
-
My clients all over the world have been getting such great results following my nutrition and training programs. They are based on my own principles and what I have spent the last couple of years trial and error to make sure they work! ✅
